The paper presents a model for auctioning ad slots in advance, which involves pricing and allocation mechanisms. This falls under the category of game theory (cs.GT) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses the implementation of the mechanism, which involves data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) and machine learning (cs.MA). Finally, the paper presents results on the efficiency and revenue of the mechanism, which falls under the category of learning theory (cs.LG).
